  "page": "Plains of the Jogos Nhai",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:502px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg/500px-92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"220\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg/750px-92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg/1000px-92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:92e7ae8aa6cabcb71e5b6f02a7301a00.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a> astride <a href=\"/index.php/Zorse\" title=\"Zorse\">zorses</a> on the plains - by Marc Simonetti ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>plains of the Jogos Nhai</b> are in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sand_Sea\" title=\"Great Sand Sea\">Great Sand Sea</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Howling_Hills\" title=\"Howling Hills\">Howling Hills</a>, north of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Shrinking_Sea\" title=\"Shrinking Sea\">Shrinking Sea</a>, and west of <a href=\"/index.php/N%27Ghai\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"N&#39;Ghai\">N'Ghai</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Bleeding_Sea\" title=\"Bleeding Sea\">Bleeding Sea</a>. To the north is <a href=\"/index.php/Leviathan_Sound\" title=\"Leviathan Sound\">Leviathan Sound</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a>, a race of nomadic mounted warriors, live in small bands on windswept plains and rolling hills. The plains are drier and less fertile than the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>, having sparse grass. The <a href=\"/index.php/Zorse\" title=\"Zorse\">zorses</a> of the Jogos Nhai eat weeds and <a href=\"/index.php/Devilgrass\" title=\"Devilgrass\">devilgrass</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Before the <a href=\"/index.php/Dry_Times\" title=\"Dry Times\">Dry Times</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a> warred with the <a href=\"/index.php/Patrimony_of_Hyrkoon\" title=\"Patrimony of Hyrkoon\">Patrimony of Hyrkoon</a> and brought thousands of Hyrkoon to the plains as <a href=\"/index.php/Slaves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slaves\">slaves</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a> has invaded the plains in multiple campaigns.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The East.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://io9.com/5954289/at-last-official-maps-of-george-rr-martins-lands-from-westeros-to-qarth\">[1]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_the_plains_of_the_jogos_nhai.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: The Plains of the Jogos Nhai.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Regions\" title=\"Template:Regions\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:Regions\" title=\"Template talk:Regions\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Regions&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nRegions of the <a href=\"/index.php/Portal:Geography\" title=\"Portal:Geography\">Known World</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.ph